# Frontend - React/Vite with nginx
FROM node:18-alpine AS frontend-builder
WORKDIR /app/frontend
COPY frontend/package*.json ./
RUN npm ci
COPY frontend/ ./
RUN npm run build

FROM nginx:alpine AS frontend
COPY --from=frontend-builder /app/frontend/dist /usr/share/nginx/html
EXPOSE 80
CMD ["nginx", "-g", "daemon off;"]

# API - Go server
FROM golang:1.21-alpine AS api-builder
WORKDIR /app/api
COPY api/go.mod api/go.sum ./
RUN go mod download
COPY api/ ./
RUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -o server .

FROM alpine:latest AS api
COPY --from=api-builder /app/api/server /usr/local/bin/server
EXPOSE 8080
CMD ["server"]

# Worker - Python Celery
FROM python:3.11-slim AS worker-builder
WORKDIR /app/worker
COPY worker/requirements.txt ./
RUN pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt

FROM python:3.11-slim AS worker
WORKDIR /app/worker
COPY --from=worker-builder /usr/local/lib/python3.11/site-packages /usr/local/lib/python3.11/site-packages
COPY worker/ ./
CMD ["celery", "-A", "main", "worker", "--loglevel=info"]
